{
  "stem": "2004.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, we were in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are in Ghetto Jezow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is now 1943-- probably the spring of 1943.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Again, I am sort of reunited-- not in so many words-- but I am reunited with my cousin, the youngest son of Jacob-- and my Uncle Jacob's wife.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were also in the-- in the ghetto of Jezow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not live in the same place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they lived-- the mother and her son lived in one apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I lived with a group of people in another apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we saw each other daily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I must say that she was very kind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whenever she could help me in any way with food, she always was there to help me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I got into-- we all were assigned work details outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was rather good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why was it good?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My job, at the time, was to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] be what they call a clothing and bedding selector.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now, this was clothing and bedding that was taken away from Jews that were previously sent away to-- either it was Treblinka or Majdanek, or any of the other places.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- it was-- it was all packed into a warehouse, whereby it was all together now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our job-- my job, together with some other people-- was to take select clothing with clothing, bedding with bedding, shoes with shoes, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, one day, while selecting the bedding-- the pillows-- I felt the pillow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I felt, in the pillow, there was some hard object.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't supposed to do it, but I opened up the pillow.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
